snippet.title: Ngothando (SSAA) | Mbuso Ndlovu
snippet.description:
Ngothando for SSAA voices and percussion by Mbuso Ndlovu. 

Ngothando is a song written in isiZulu, and is a message to the world that it is only through love that we can conquer the barriers that stand between us. Beautiful and accessible, this is a moving work especially meaningful for our times.

Purchase the music: https://giamusic.com/resource/ngothando-ssaa-printed-music-ww2119

Also available for SATB voicing: https://giamusic.com/resource/ngothando-print-ww1724
